[p]Salutations Victorians!
[/p][p]Lo and behold we did do one more hotfix! Aimed at primarily fixing the reported wages issue and monopolies not working correctly.
[/p][p]Otherwise, I hope I don’t jinx it again, we shouldn’t have more hotfixes on the horizon but will see you soon!
[/p][p]Check out the full patchnotes below. Checksum is `43af`.
[/p][p]As always please report any bugs on [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/forums/victoria-3-bug-reports.1114/"]our bug reporting forums[/url][/u]! We have also updated the [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/known-issues-update-1-10.1859597/"]Known Issues post for 1.10[/url][/u] with any fixed issues!
[/p][p]The following changes have been made to the game compared to 1.10.5:[/p][h2]Bugfixes[/h2][list][*][p]Fixed a bug where buildings would periodically reset their wages back to baseline, most noticeable as all buildings paying out the same wage at the start of the game[/p][/*][*][p]Fixed a bug where construction of buildings monopolized by companies could be blocked by incorrect validation of who holds the monopoly[/p][/*][*][p]Fixed a bug where autonomous construction could sometimes be blocked by the economy of scale factor overriding other, more critical factors such as whether there is actually workforce available in the state[/p][/*][*][p]Fixed a bug where the ai_evaluate_autonomous_construction console command was partially printing data for government construction, resulting in incorrect values
[/p][/*][/list][p][b]Previous Patchnotes[/b][/p][p][u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/developer-diary/victoria-3-dev-diary-160-national-awakening-update-1-10-now-live.1859612/"]1.10.0[/url][/u] | [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-10-1-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1860263/"]1.10.1[/url][/u] | [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-10-2-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1860447/"]1.10.2[/url][/u] | [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-10-3-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1861262/"]1.10.3[/url][/u] | [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-10-4-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1861603/"]1.10.4[/url][/u] | [u][url="https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/threads/hotfix-1-10-5-is-now-live-not-for-problem-reports.1862385/"]1.10.5[/url][/u][/p]